videos.description: Tar heels QB Brandon Harris attempts a pass deep but CB Bryce Hall snatches the interception and returns it 36 yards.
videos.headline: Virginia defense stout so far

videos.description: QB Kurt Benkert completes a pass to TE Evan Butts who rolls over a defender for the touchdown. Initially ruled short but replay confirmed it to be a touchdown.
videos.headline: Virginia extends lead with TD

videos.description: Michael Carter burst through the defense and speeds up the field for a 56-yard gain.
videos.headline: Freshman gives the Tar Heels life

videos.description: RB Michael Carter runs it in for 1-yard touchdown after his big run on the previous play.
videos.headline: North Carolina scores their first TD

videos.description: QB Brandon Harris throws it deep and is intercepted by Chris Moore who returns it 8 yards.
videos.headline: Tar Heels commit another turnover

videos.description: Michael Carter takes the hand off and and just outruns the Virginia defense for a 47-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Freshman RB putting on a show

videos.description: QB Kurt Benkert finds WR Olamide Zaccheaus on a short pass and he explodes up the sideline for an 81-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Virginia responds with long TD

videos.description: QB Brandon Harris is under pressure and he launches the ball down field only to be intercepted by CB Brenton Nelson for a 12-yard return.
videos.headline: Tar Heels QB Harris throws 3rd interception

videos.description: Kurt Benkert is sacked by Malik Carney who forces the fumble and it is recovered by the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Virginia loses critical fumble
